<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>
    The information used on this site will only be used to support the Jesse P. Roland Memorial Toys for Tots Benefit online raffle. 
    Your information is required to contact you if you
    are a winner and match your donation to your ticket selections. Your personal information
    will not be used for any other purpose and will not be distributed, sold or provided outside
    of this event.
</p>
<p>
    On the Toys for Tots donation page there is a separate Privacy Policy that governs their use
    of your information. We have chosen to have supporters send money directly to Toys for Tots via the
    Jesse P. Roland Memorial Toys for Tots Benefit Donation Page to avoid transferring funds between the organizers and their
    personal accounts back to Toys for Tots.
</p>
